cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.DS

This paper deals with the problem of detecting Android malware using machine learning techniques, specifically clustering. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other likely categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), as the paper involves developing a novel clustering method to improve the accuracy of malware detection.
